<taxonomicName box="[1324,1436,1477,1502]" class="Arachnida" family="Hydryphantidae" genus="Hydryphantes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dispar">
<emphasis box="[1324,1436,1477,1502]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">H. dispar</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is obviously a rare, but widely distributed pond-dwelling species.
